<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It used to be that the big investment banking =
was the generic way to become rich. If you were a young person with fancy c=
redentials, a strong desire for money, and no strong preferences or interes=
ts, it was kind of natural to go to a bank. =E2=80=9COddly enough,=E2=80=9D=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34928529.256352/a=
HR0cHM6Ly9ib29rcy5nb29nbGUuY29tL2Jvb2tzP2lkPUxwUzlBd0FBUUJBSiZwZz1QVDQzJmxw=
