: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bord=
er-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #cc=
c;">Michael Lewis wrote</a> of his first day as a Salomon Brothers=C2=A0bon=
d salesman with a Princeton art history degree,=C2=A0=E2=80=9CI didn=E2=80=
=99t really imagine I was going to work, more as if I were going to collect=
 lottery winnings.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That was in 1985, and the next two decades or =
so were good, dynamic, lucrative times for the big investment banks. They d=
ominated finance, and they innovated, building new products that increased =
their dominance and brought in lots of money.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But now it is 2024 and <a href=3D"https://link=
.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34928529.256352/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZ=
XJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMTItMjIvd2FsbC1zdHJlZXQtaXMtbm8tZnVu=
LWFueW1vcmU_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQwNDI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1=
fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjQwNDA0JnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dW=
Zm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB424517f0" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">things have changed</a>. Corp=
orate dealmaking is dominated by private equity firms, buyout financing is =
increasingly done by private credit, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/34928529.256352/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDItMDcvaGVkZ2UtZnVuZHMtYXJlLWRlYWxlcnMtbm93P2NtcGl=
kPUJCRDA0MDQyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbG=
V0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDQwNCZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cB2f89346c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">trading</a> is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.b=
loombergbusiness.com/click/34928529.256352/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNv=
bS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDMtMDQvdHJhZGluZy1kZXNrcy10cmFkZS1sZXNzLWx=
