mY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6c0b30c1" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"i=
temscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none =
!important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-=
bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">increasingly</a> done by hedg=
e funds and proprietary trading firms. Those are the places to make a lot o=
