eta or Alphabet, not Goldman Sachs.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Still, =E2=80=9CWall Street=E2=80=9D (meaning =
big investment banks) has retained its image as a generic wealth creator, w=
hich can lead to disappointment. At the New York Post, <a href=3D"https://l=
ink.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34928529.256352/aHR0cHM6Ly9ueXBvc3QuY2=
9tLzIwMjQvMDQvMDQvYnVzaW5lc3MvanVuaW9yLWJhbmtlcnMtc2F5LXRoZXlsbC1xdWl0LWFmd=
GVyLWJvbnVzZXMtZmFsbC8/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdfdd7edb" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">Lydia Moy=
nihan reports</a> that =E2=80=9Chundreds of thousands of junior bankers are=
 cutting back after their bonuses were a bust this year,=E2=80=9D with anec=
dotes like this:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">One vice president at a large firm who has a o=
ne bedroom in the West Village, albeit a walkup, said after receiving even =
less this year than he did last year, he has tried to scale back the number=
 of times he eats out to two nights a week instead of three or four.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At his favorite spots =E2=80=94 Carbone where =
branzino costs $95, Dante=E2=80=99s where veal Milanese is $60 and Saint Th=
eo=E2=80=99s where lamb chops are $68 =E2=80=94 a dinner tab can quickly ba=
lloon to $300 or more and a drinks tab can easily hit $100 for a date. =E2=
=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CFirst year employees are only making =
a $100,000 salary in New York City. They rely on a decent bonus to pay thei=
r rent,=E2=80=9D a source in his 60s, who has been working as a banker for =
four decades, said.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The source, who noted the median Manhattan ren=
t is $4,257 according to a StreetEasy study from February said he =E2=80=9C=
felt for the kids.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">What is the world coming to when the investmen=
t banking kids can=E2=80=99t even afford the branzino at Carbone.</p>
